### 想要排除某些信息
[官方文档](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/logstash/5.4/event-dependent-configuration.html#conditionals)


```
if "_grokparsefailure" not in [tags] {
        if [sqlDuring] < 5 {
                 drop {}
         }
}
else {
        drop {}
}
```

